Titolo: Alone in the Dark: Illumination

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Alone in the Dark: Illumination is the sixth installment of the survival horror video game series under the same title by Atari SA. It's also the last title in the series to be published by Atari as the IP has since been acquired by THQ Nordic. The game is developed by Pure FPS for Windows and is the series' first installment to be played online and in a cooperative setting. The game was panned heavily.